name: Ford Falcon
description:
King of urban roads. For both family and sports, popular in several countries around the globe. Today, justa another machine in the Junkyard Universe.

Digital illustration, 300 dpi, 4245 x 5118  pixels

Collection: Universo Chatarra Deluxe Edition
A special collection of vintage cars from around the world, as depicted in the Universo Chatarra (Junkyard Universe) series: old-fashioned, dystopic, and strangely glamorous floating machines.

By Alejandro Burdisio (Burda), January 19th, 2022.
